cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual place recognition and proposes a CNN-based approach for the same. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the proposed approach involves learning domain-invariant features and using weakly supervised ranking loss. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes an attention mechanism to focus on relevant features and improve performance. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with matching images from different domains. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper involves matching query images with relevant instances from a gallery database.
